    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AddBooking
    Command to add a new booking to the flight booking system.
    AddCustomer
    Command to add a new customer to the flight booking system.
    AddCustomerWindow
    The AddCustomerWindow class provides a graphical user interface for adding a new customer.
    AddFlight
    Command to add a new flight to the flight booking system.
    AddFlightWindow
    The AddFlightWindow class provides a graphical user interface for adding a new flight.
    Booking
    The Booking class represents a booking in the flight booking system.
    BookingDataManager
    Manages the loading and storing of booking data.
    CancelBooking
    Command to cancel a booking in the flight booking system.
    CancelBookingWindow
    The CancelBookingWindow class provides a graphical user interface for canceling a booking.
    Command
    Interface for commands in the flight booking system.
    CommandParser
     
    Customer
    The Customer class represents a customer in the booking system.
    CustomerTest
     
    DeleteCustomer
    Command to delete a customer from the flight booking system.
    DeleteCustomerWindow
    The DeleteCustomerWindow class provides a graphical user interface for deleting a customer.
    DeleteFlight
    Command to mark a flight as inactive in the flight booking system.
    DeleteFlightWindow
     
    EditBooking
    Command to edit an existing booking in the flight booking system.
    Flight
    The Flight class represents a flight in the booking system.
    FlightBookingSystem
    The FlightBookingSystem class manages flights, customers, and bookings.
    FlightBookingSystemException
    FlightBookingSystemException extends Exception class and is a custom exception that is used to notify the user about errors or invalid commands.
    FlightTest
     
    Help
    Command to display help message.
    IssueBookingWindow
    The IssueBookingWindow class provides a graphical user interface for issuing a new booking.
    ListCustomers
    Command to list all customers in the flight booking system.
    ListFlights
    Command to list all flights in the flight booking system.
    LoadGUI
    Command to load the GUI.
    Main
     
    MainWindow
    The MainWindow class provides the main graphical user interface for the flight booking management system.
    ShowCustomer
    Command to show the details of a specific customer.
    ShowFlight
    Command to show the details of a specific flight.
    UpdateFlightWindow
    The UpdateFlightWindow class provides a graphical user interface for updating a flight booking.
